    "rendered": "<p>Current work, living systems, and useful experiments Community infrastructure, AI learning systems, keynote portals, and cultural field notes. I build things that help people meet the future without losing the plot: public AI communities, practical training, talks that become portals, and long-running story systems that make technology feel human again. Book a keynote Work with <a class=\"more-link\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/recent-projects-include/\">Read More &#8230;</a></p>\n",
